1
00:00:00,916 --> 00:00:04,166
When I reached the prison,
they took me to the interrogator

2
00:00:05,333 --> 00:00:08,625
He saw the slip and
asked, Why did you argue?

3
00:00:09,125 --> 00:00:12,000
I told him I didn't argue
over anything, I'm a taxi driver

4
00:00:13,458 --> 00:00:16,250
And the taxi is on the
street, anyone can ride

5
00:00:16,916 --> 00:00:19,083
Whether a woman or a man

6
00:00:19,666 --> 00:00:21,750
Anyone can ride,
that's why it's a taxi

7
00:00:22,291 --> 00:00:24,208
He said, Without a
<i>mahram</i>, it's forbidden

8
00:00:25,416 --> 00:00:28,583
She was alone, and I
argued with him, so he wrote

9
00:00:29,166 --> 00:00:31,833
On the slip: Carries
a woman alone

10
00:00:31,875 --> 00:00:33,916
And he says, We'll quit
working and sit at home

11
00:00:33,958 --> 00:00:37,250
The interrogator asked me about that, and I told
him, Yes, then we'll quit working and sit at home

12
00:00:37,291 --> 00:00:38,208
Because our work is the taxi

13
00:00:39,833 --> 00:00:44,041
He told the ISIS member,
Take him to prison

14
00:00:46,083 --> 00:00:47,666
And whip him 100 lashes

15
00:00:48,625 --> 00:00:51,416
So the ISIS member took
me to the prison upstairs

16
00:00:51,458 --> 00:00:53,541
Made me go up, and I
stayed until the second day

17
00:00:56,333 --> 00:01:00,583
They called him Abu
Hurayra, not by his name

18
00:01:01,083 --> 00:01:03,500
Each of them had a nom de
guerre they used for themselves

19
00:01:03,541 --> 00:01:05,458
Abu So-and-so... Abu Hurayra

20
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:08,250
The one who interrogated
me was called Abu Hurayra

21
00:01:09,958 --> 00:01:11,833
Bearded ISIS member

22
00:01:12,333 --> 00:01:13,416
Interrogator

23
00:01:15,041 --> 00:01:18,708
Interviewer: What kind of
questions did the interrogator ask?

24
00:01:20,791 --> 00:01:22,333
He asked me for my ID

25
00:01:22,333 --> 00:01:24,500
He asked, What did they
take from you? I told him, My ID

26
00:01:25,791 --> 00:01:27,375
Then he asked, he
said, Why did they take it?

27
00:01:28,166 --> 00:01:31,291
I answered, I told him, Because
of a woman who was alone

28
00:01:31,333 --> 00:01:33,208
She was riding
with me in the car
